BeyondTrust Splunk App for Remote Support
Version 1.0.0
June 2021

This Application includes Dashboards that are pre-configured for Remote Support

Requirements:
1- Remote Support integration for Splunk with Middleware Engine
2- Corresponding Data Input(See documentation https://www.beyondtrust.com/docs/remote-support/how-to/index.htm )
3- Events in Splunk from Remote Support


You can set either set source=password_safe or sourcetype=beyondtrust at the Password Safe Connector level, or at the Data Input level.

Each report in the Dashboard filter data like this:  (sourcetype=beyondtrust_rs_syslog_cim) index=idx_beyondtrust

It is possible to quickly edit each report to replace with desired source, sourcetype, or index.

For any question or feedback, please contact Integrations@beyondtrust.com
 